item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Backstreet Boys - A Night Out With the Backstreet Boys (Full Concert)
item.description:
​

A Night Out with the Backstreet Boys is an unplugged acoustic concert show performed by the Backstreet Boys. It was recorded live at Viva Television in Cologne, Germany on March 28, 1998. It was first released in VHS format with a bonus CD titled Selections from A Night Out with the Backstreet Boys, and was released later on DVD on November 7, 2000.

Two songs performed and included in this album, "Where Can We Go From Here?" and "Who Do You Love", were never released as studio recordings.

Audio ripped directly from the official DVD release.
This is the full concert -- not the "selections" CD.​

1. Who Do You Love
2. As Long As You Love Me
3. 10,000 Promises
4. That's What She Said/Where Can We Go From Here? (Brian solo)
5. Lay Down Beside Me (A.J. solo)
6. I Need You Tonight (Early Version) [Nick's solo]
7. My Heart Stays With You (Howie's solo)
8. Kevin's Solo (Untitled)
9. Like A Child
10. All I Have To Give
11. If I Don't Have You/I'll Never Break Your Heart
12 Quit Playing Games (With My Heart)
13. Let's Have A Party (Outro)
